Pattaya food delivery for high cuisine standards in lovely surroundings

This is one of Thailand's top holiday destinations. It's situated on the eastern side of the sea, and is stunningly pretty but has been developed into a luxury resort that still fits with the beautiful surroundings. So, food here is wonderful, sophisticated and varied. The local Thai cuisine is amazing, but here's also a really good range of Chinese, Indian, Malaysian and Western cuisine style available too. If you're into fitness and health, this is also a resort that has lots of great vegetarian and healthy food choices too, due to the many Spa hotels situated here.

Pattaya's finest restaurants to order online from

If you like Vegetarian, then you must try the well known, top level, 'Five Star J Restaurant,' which has some delicious food for Vegetarians and Vegans. 'Rim Talay,' meanwhile is one of the best Thai restaurants, with delicate dishes and spicy dishes to try that will delight. Or for something unusual, try 'Linda's Restaurant,' which has Norwegian dishes as well as some great versions of Italian pasta dishes. Or for a classic steak dinner, why not try, 'News Steaks and Grills,' it's one of the best!

Thai food at it's best and a whole lot more in Pattaya

The biggest thing about food in Pattaya is the quality. However, Thai food reigns supreme here. Not only is it the local cuisine, but the standard is incredibly high. It's also one of the loveliest cuisines in the world, and popular! Equally popular though, is Indian food. Rich, spicy and with lots of vegetarian options, it works well with the hot surroundings. It's also a great cuisine for celebrations, and with so many holiday makers and visitors on honeymoon, or enjoying anniversaries and birthdays, Indian cuisine is great. Chinese food is also of an excellent standard, and is a great option for those who love tasty, but not so hot food!
